迪斯、梁柏廷，到底哪一個才是真名？TL說：「我原名叫『梁家進』，到2011年爸爸有啲毛病，就嚟過身，我嗰時簽咗公司就嚟出道，公司就帶咗我去睇相，改咗『梁迪斯』，連身份證都改埋。」身份證改名為爸爸沖喜後，他又與當時唱片公司商討用「梁柏廷」作出道藝名，可惜未出道就因「肛交勒索案」罪成入獄26個月。刑滿後，他又改名「韓梓亮」：「今次冇睇相，我好鍾意韓國，『梓』就係木加個辛字，好似人只要努力就會建立到一舊木，努力就會發光發熱。」<br />\n<br />\n請大家記住TL !<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f037d22c45c8124df1cc73c6aa4de1bc411ee5","tid":933374,"uid":370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9a606b0a1f3387d0bc6c2cc4077f2814a2e85bc","tid":933374,"uid":171594,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"60181a44446d50d20cb446f3c11209ff05d6fecc","tid":933374,"uid":44243,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"223eb9a1eab0d6d80f1ea934f4c908f2a73d89b7","tid":933374,"uid":202340,"like":209,"dislike":3,"score":206,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T07:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VqUqRSA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVqUqRSA.png&h=18f5d076&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T12:32:30.000Z","msg":"講野語氣同tl一樣<br />\n柒過奸奸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T12:52:09.000Z","msg":"會唔會有人俾定個fb ac密碼朋友知呀<br />\n一出事即刻出到post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話自己經理人都合理啲<br />\n當人傻架咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:27:28.000Z","msg":"Legacy Contact?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1038eef5457bca7ea5a9435fe182359db2e6955e","tid":933374,"uid":152123,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c8f6e27b3a733efc1a7e7c12e7cf942932ca69a","tid":933374,"uid":56716,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T13:12:23.000Z","msg":"@手卷<br />\n一齊去探TL？好擔心佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:29:15.000Z","msg":"笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8889d3ae3a3856a30a3432a1cb4b0ff60ab93f","tid":933374,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:30:48.000Z","msg":"呀TL 難得你話係連登得到咁多歡樂 仲走上嚟多謝大家 點解仲要睇唔開自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f86072d88c87bc6fdbe4d75f9d9b05da1789bdbe","tid":933374,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:40:32.000Z","msg":"自細跟住好憎佢嘅阿媽生活，被鬧賤種、乞兒，至今攞住死鬼老竇部份遺產闖一番事業，命途未算最坎坷嘅！<br />\n<br />\n真面目<br />\n同聲同氣　劉公子同囚赤柱　勒索同志歌手出獄：叫我陪佢瞓<br />\n13年時準備出道做歌手的梁迪斯（原名梁家進，又名梁柏廷），因與一男同志發生肛交後勒索對方 25萬，結果勒索罪成，最終被判入獄 2年。<br />\n<br />\n當年被大字標題寫到「樂壇新秀涉肛交勒索」，出獄後的梁迪斯改名換姓韓梓亮（ TL），死心不息再向樂壇發展。週日（ 6日）接受訪問：「𠵱家好好彩，可以做番歌手重新出道。」仲大爆與劉公子同囚赤柱的秘聞。<br />\n<br />\n「急住搵錢交租，喺程式上識咗啲人，上咗嚟我屋企。初頭真係無諗過呃佢錢，係佢真係雞姦咗我，咁然後我就諗歪咗，導致俾人告恐嚇勒索。自己真係錯咗。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://bimg.hitttt.com/dd8_20160309/9450_1765cae45bf48b7e6382ba1c80532429_W1259_025_002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbimg.hitttt.com%2Fdd8_20160309%2F9450_1765cae45bf48b7e6382ba1c80532429_W1259_025_002.jpg&h=9a28cd3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現已改名換姓叫韓梓亮的他，係江湖二代，爸爸沙膽雄當年活躍佐敦一帶，更是剛過身的 14K要員鬍鬚勇頭馬之一，惜 12年因病離世。<br />\n<br />\n13年因勒索男同志 25萬而被判入獄 2年 2個月，與母親關係甚差嘅韓梓亮全程冇親人去探過監。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://bimg.hitttt.com/dd8_20160309/1300_1765cae45bf48b7e6382ba1c80532429_W1259_025_004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbimg.hitttt.com%2Fdd8_20160309%2F1300_1765cae45bf48b7e6382ba1c80532429_W1259_025_004.jpg&h=4779d150&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓梓亮爸爸沙膽雄（右一）曾介紹過唔少藝人前輩畀囝囝識，勒索事件發生後，韓梓亮曾經搵過部份前輩出嚟食飯兼攞意見（網上圖片）"},{"pid":"9b48622821b26e3d7b632f9e754d6b9a257261c5","tid":933374,"uid":22349,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://bimg.hitttt.com/dd8_20160309/9450_1765cae45bf48b7e6382ba1c80532429_W1259_025_002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbimg.hitttt.com%2Fdd8_20160309%2F9450_1765cae45bf48b7e6382ba1c80532429_W1259_025_002.jpg&h=9a28cd3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講到 13年被男同志雞姦，韓梓亮不禁流眼淚，喊住謂：「真係好痛。」"},{"pid":"16e51d44e182891afa1827321ea5adee3ceec54b","tid":933374,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T15:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/KsY7ofC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKsY7ofC.png&h=8d8c9716&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0528b2a8b44c43ec823e5e93513dbc7c644a8d76","tid":933374,"uid":52824,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T15:07:09.000Z","msg":"屎眼歌手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8487e01179f564ad828eaaa6dc452af31de42ecd","tid":933374,"uid":145277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"340927ffc712187b4b6fb1632b211fa122973aa9","tid":933374,"uid":4525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T13:24:36.000Z","msg":"香港樂壇最後既希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"其實點解連登會推佢上神壇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1066025eceb0480a046854d403db60aa6fb124c","tid":933374,"uid":22349,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8487e01179f564ad828eaaa6dc452af31de42ecd","tid":933374,"uid":145277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"340927ffc712187b4b6fb1632b211fa122973aa9","tid":933374,"uid":4525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T13:24:36.000Z","msg":"香港樂壇最後既希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass